summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Romanian judicial institutions management system. Backend API works correctly with 232 institutions, proper alphabetical sorting, and key-name structure. Frontend loads with modern design, searchable dropdown, and theme toggle functionality.

flaky_endpoints.issue: SOAP API calls to just.ro timeout after 30 seconds
flaky_endpoints.impact: Search functionality may be slow or fail intermittently
flaky_endpoints.note: External dependency issue, not application bug

passed_tests: API /api/institutii returns 232 institutions with key-name pairs
Institutions are sorted alphabetically by name
Landing page loads with modern design and Inter font
Public search page loads correctly at /search
Searchable dropdown shows institution names (not API keys)
Institution dropdown filters correctly (Alba search returned 14 results)
Form inputs work correctly (case number, party name)
Clean design with proper spacing and typography
Authentication properly required for monitoring endpoints
Error handling works correctly for invalid date formats
Bulk search and CSV upload interfaces present

success_percentage.backend: 90% (9/10 tests passed - 1 timeout due to external SOAP API)
success_percentage.frontend: 100% (all UI elements and functionality working correctly)
